item.title: C Library
item.description: #define OK 0 #define NO_INPUT 1 #define TOO_LONG 2 static int testFunc(int a, int b) { if(a == b) return OK; else if(a > b) return NO_INPUT; else return TOO_LONG; } double testTwo(char* buffer, int length) { for(int i = 0; i < length; i++) { buffer[i] = i; } return 0.9; }
